  "witness_en": "The Pharisee thought: if this man were a prophet, he would know who is touching him. But Jesus said to the woman: your sins are forgiven; your faith has saved you. She loved much because she knew how much she had been forgiven. Only those who deeply know their need of grace can love most deeply.",
