  "prayer": "主，你叫了马利亚的名字，她立刻认出了你。谢谢你也知道我的名字。帮助我像她一样成为你复活的忠心见证人。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "The freed becomes the most faithful witness",
  "summary_en": "Seven demons were driven out of her; thereafter she followed Jesus, was present at the cross and the empty tomb, and was the first witness of the resurrection.",
  "witness_en": "She was present at Jesus' loneliest moments—at the cross, by the tomb. On resurrection morning she came seeking Jesus, and He called her name: Mary. In that moment of being named, she recognized Him. The one changed by love is the most faithful witness.",
