  "lesson_en": "The combination of talent and humbly receiving correction",
  "summary_en": "An eloquent man from Alexandria, mighty in the Scriptures and fervent in preaching, who knew only John's baptism; after Priscilla and Aquila taught him privately, he became a more powerful preacher.",
