  "witness_en": "He was on the list of the twelve apostles together with Matthew—one a tax collector for the Roman Empire, the other a revolutionary resisting Rome. Jesus deliberately put these two together. This is the most unlikely reconciliation. The mystery of the kingdom: people who hated each other became brothers through Jesus. His zeal did not disappear; only its object changed from politics to God's kingdom.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Simon the Zealot's zeal was redirected by You. Help me give all my passion to You, letting You decide where it should point. Amen.",
