  "witness_en": "Peter said: one must be chosen from those who have accompanied us. Matthias was such a man—always following, never in the spotlight, never self-promoting, just there. Then God's choice fell on him. His story tells us: faithful following is itself the qualification. You need not be famous, only present.",
