  "witness_en": "Jacob prayed for him: I wait for Your salvation, O LORD! This is a sigh—as if Jacob already foresaw this tribe would go astray. The title of greatest potential sometimes comes with the deepest temptation. The tribe of Dan's story reminds us: God-given potential needs obedience to be realized, or it becomes a footnote.",
