  "witness_en": "'The LORD our God, the LORD is one' (Deut 6:4), yet baptizing into the one 'name' of the Father, Son, and Spirit (Matt 28:19). The Father sends, the Son accomplishes, the Spirit applies—the same God, three persons, at work in history and in your life and mine. Knowing His works gives worship a root and foundation.",
