  "ref": "约296–373年·亚历山大主教",
  "summary": "尼西亚会议的旗手，一生对抗否认基督完全神性的阿里乌派。屡遭放逐五次，几乎与整个时代为敌，被称「Athanasius contra mundum（亚他那修独抗世界）」。著《论道成肉身》，坚立「子与父同质」的正统信仰。",
  "witness": "当主流、皇权、多数都偏向异端时，他宁可独自站立，因为真理不在乎人多。",
  "follow": [
   "在举世偏离时仍独自持守「基督完全是神」的真理",
   "五次被放逐仍不妥协，真理不随多数转移",
   "以《论道成肉身》正面阐明救恩的根基"
  ],
  "caution": [],
  "applications": [
   "当主流、多数、权势都偏向错误，你敢不敢像亚他那修一样独自站立？",
   "真理不在乎人多——你今天有没有为合圣经的立场而不怕孤立？",
   "基督完全是神，这不是细节而是救恩的根基，务要守住",
   "今天为持守真道却被孤立的人祷告，也求神给你这份骨气"
  ],
  "scriptures": [],
  "prayer": "主啊，当举世偏离时，亚他那修独抗世界持守你儿子的神性。求你赐我这样的勇气与骨气，在多数与权势都偏向错误时，仍单单顺服你的话，宁可孤立也不妥协真理。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "Standing alone against the world, holding to Christ's deity",
  "summary_en": "The standard-bearer of the Council of Nicaea, who fought all his life against the Arians who denied Christ's full deity. Exiled five times, nearly at odds with his whole age, he was called 'Athanasius contra mundum (Athanasius against the world).' He wrote 'On the Incarnation,' establishing the orthodox faith that 'the Son is of the same substance as the Father.'",
  "witness_en": "When the mainstream, the imperial power, and the majority all leaned toward heresy, he would rather stand alone, because truth does not depend on numbers.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, when the whole world strayed, Athanasius stood against the world holding to Your Son's deity. Give me such courage and backbone, that when majority and power both lean toward error, I may still obey Your word alone, preferring isolation to compromising the truth. Amen.",
  "follow_en": [
   "Holding alone to the truth that 'Christ is fully God' when the whole world had strayed",
   "Not compromising though exiled five times—truth does not shift with the majority",
   "Positively expounding the foundation of salvation with 'On the Incarnation'"
  ],
