  "lesson_en": "The ascended Christ still cares for us with tenderness",
  "summary_en": "A Puritan Independent leader, president of Magdalen College Oxford, member of the Westminster Assembly, a theological heavyweight ranked with John Owen. His classic 'The Heart of Christ in Heaven' depicts the ascended Christ still caring for weak saints on earth with a tender heart—even when we suffer, are weak, or fall, our Savior in heaven loves us all the more tenderly.",
