  "prayer_en": "Lord Jesus, You ascended to heaven, yet Your heart is all the more tender toward weak me on earth. Through Goodwin make me deeply know Your love, not fleeing You when I fall and am weak but drawing nearer; let Your caring heart be my real comfort. Amen.",
