  "witness_en": "Manoah and his wife's witness lies in humbly receiving God's revelation. His wife received the promise first, and Manoah did not despise it but prayed: 'Please let the man of God come again to us and teach us what to do with the child who is to be born.' When the Angel did a wondrous thing, ascending in the flame, they fell on their faces, recognizing this was God Himself coming. They witnessed: the deliverer's birth was wholly from God's own initiative of revelation and grace.",
