  "prayer": "主啊，加百列忠心传递祢的话，带下安慰与盼望。求祢使我也作祢忠实的信使，准确传讲祢的真理，以祢的话安慰惧怕的人，深信在祢没有难成的事。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "Faithfully conveying God's word, neither adding nor subtracting",
  "summary_en": "An angel standing in God's presence, who conveyed God's message to Daniel, Zechariah, and Mary, announcing the key moments of the plan of salvation.",
  "witness_en": "Gabriel is God's messenger, the one who 'stands in the presence of God.' He announced John the Baptist's birth to Zechariah and Christ's birth to Mary: 'Nothing will be impossible with God.' He faithfully conveyed God's word, neither adding nor subtracting, and with comfort: 'Do not be afraid, Mary, for you have found favor with God.' Gabriel represents all who serve faithfully, obey simply, and convey God's word accurately—greatness is not in how important you are, but in whose message you carry.",
