  "lesson_en": "A passed-over brother, each has his place",
  "summary_en": "Jesse's second son, David's brother.",
  "witness_en": "Abinadab was Jesse's second son and David's brother. When Samuel anointed a king he too passed before Samuel, yet God did not choose him. He later served in Saul's army. God's choice is not by birth order or appearance; the passed-over also have their own duty to keep.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Abinadab was passed over, yet David was chosen. Make me, when passed over, still content in my duty, without jealousy, firmly trusting Your choice has its own good purpose. Amen.",
