  "witness_en": "Chileab was a son of David and Abigail, the second born. Scripture mentions him only once in the list of David's sons, with no further record—he may have died young. In the illustrious royal house, he is one nearly forgotten—yet the forgotten by people are not forgotten by God.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Chileab was nearly forgotten by people, yet You remembered him. Make me live not to be remembered by people but to be remembered by You, and teach me to treasure every seemingly ordinary life. Amen.",
