  "witness_en": "Jehu was the son of the seer Hanani, who both rebuked Jehoshaphat for allying with the wicked king Ahab, and affirmed his good of 'removing the Asherah poles and setting his heart to seek God.' His rebuke had measure and fairness—pointing out the wrong, yet also seeing the good.",
