  "summary_en": "A false prophet hired to intimidate Nehemiah.",
  "witness_en": "This Shemaiah was bought off by Tobiah and Sanballat, feigning a warning for Nehemiah to hide in the temple for safety, hoping to lead him to break the rules and ruin his name. But Nehemiah discerned that 'God had not sent him' and refused to fall for it. Advice wrapped in a spiritual cloak also needs to be tested for truth.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Nehemiah saw through Shemaiah's hired scheme. Give me a discerning spirit, not deceived by intimidation and advice in a spiritual cloak, walking steadily in Your will. Amen.",
