  "prayer": "主啊，腓立比狱卒一夜之间全家归向祢。求祢使我真心寻求救恩、立刻回应，并带领我的家一同信靠、服事祢。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "Overnight, from jailer to believer",
  "summary_en": "The jailer who believed because of the earthquake and was baptized with his whole household.",
  "witness_en": "He was the jailer of Philippi, who at midnight when a great earthquake shook all the doors open, thinking the prisoners had escaped, was about to kill himself. Paul loudly stopped him. Trembling, he fell down and asked 'what must I do to be saved,' and that night his whole household believed and was baptized, and he washed Paul and Silas' wounds and set food before them. God's salvation can turn a person's whole family around overnight.",
