  "prayer": "主啊，祢释放了那被利用牟利的使女。求祢使我看重人的得释放过于其用处，为被辖制的人争取自由，奉祢的名抵挡黑暗。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "Being set free surpasses being used",
  "summary_en": "The slave girl from whom Paul cast out a spirit of divination.",
  "witness_en": "She was a slave girl in Philippi possessed by a spirit of divination, by which her masters gained much profit from fortune-telling. She followed Paul crying out for many days, and Paul cast out the spirit in the name of Jesus. She was set free, but her masters, their hope of gain cut off, angrily accused Paul. In the Lord's eyes, a person's being set free is far more precious than being used to earn money.",
