  "witness_en": "Secundus was a Thessalonian, one of Paul's companions on his last journey, traveling with Aristarchus and others. He has no astonishing deeds, yet was one of the faithful co-workers who accompanied and escorted the apostle all the way. To walk with someone to the end is itself a kind of faithfulness.",
