  "scriptures": [
   "林前1:1",
   "徒18:17"
  ],
  "prayer": "主啊，祢把会堂主管所提尼变成了保罗的同工。求祢使我相信祢恩典的翻转大能，不轻看任何人，也甘心被祢更新使用。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "From opponent to co-worker, grace turns a life around",
  "summary_en": "The brother who co-signed a letter with Paul.",
  "witness_en": "Sosthenes was originally the ruler of the synagogue in Corinth, once beaten before the judgment seat; yet later he became a Christian, co-signing with Paul the letter to the Corinthian church. God's grace can turn a former opponent into a present co-worker—no one is beyond the reach of grace.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, You turned the synagogue ruler Sosthenes into Paul's co-worker. Make me trust the turning power of Your grace, not despising anyone, and willingly be renewed and used by You. Amen.",
