  "summary_en": "Timothy's grandmother, of genuine faith.",
  "witness_en": "Lois was Timothy's grandmother, whose 'sincere faith' first dwelt in her own heart, then was passed to her daughter Eunice, and on to her grandson Timothy. Faith handed down through three generations produced a faithful gospel co-worker. A spiritual inheritance can be passed on like this, generation by generation.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Lois' faith passed through three generations and bore fruit in Timothy. Make me hold sincere faith, a spiritual example to children and grandchildren, passing faith down generation by generation. Amen.",
