  "prayer": "主啊，希勒斯名列勇士，忠心征战。求祢使我甘作团队中默默尽忠的一员，与众同心，深知祢记念每一个忠心的人。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "A faithful member on the roll of mighty men",
  "summary_en": "A Paltite, one of David's mighty men.",
  "witness_en": "Helez was one of David's mighty men (a Paltite/Pelonite), listed among the warriors who fought for David. He has no solo deed detailed, yet by loyalty and bravery joined the ranks of heroes. Those who quietly do their duty in the team, God records each of their names.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Helez was on the roll of mighty men, faithfully fighting. Make me willingly a quietly faithful member, of one heart with others, knowing You remember every faithful one. Amen.",
