  "summary": "保罗上诉的罗马皇帝（该撒），传统上保罗殉道时期的皇帝。",
  "witness": "尼禄是保罗上诉的罗马皇帝，传统上保罗与彼得都在他的逼迫中殉道。这位以残暴著称的皇帝想用火与刀扑灭信仰，福音却越烧越旺。最凶猛的逼迫，也挡不住神国的扩展。",
  "follow": [],
  "caution": [
   "以权力与暴力逼迫信仰",
   "以为能用强权扑灭真理"
  ],
  "applications": [
   "在逼迫与压力中持守信仰，不退缩",
   "相信福音的能力胜过一切强权",
   "为今日受逼迫的信徒祷告"
  ],
  "scriptures": [
   "徒25:11",
   "提后4:16-17"
  ],
  "prayer": "主啊，尼禄的逼迫烧不尽祢的福音。求祢坚固一切在压力与逼迫中的信徒，使我深信祢的国度胜过世上一切强权。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "The fire of persecution cannot burn up the gospel",
  "summary_en": "The Roman emperor (Caesar) to whom Paul appealed, traditionally the emperor at Paul's martyrdom.",
  "witness_en": "Nero was the Roman emperor to whom Paul appealed; traditionally both Paul and Peter were martyred under his persecution. This emperor, known for cruelty, tried to extinguish the faith by fire and sword, yet the gospel burned all the brighter. The fiercest persecution cannot stop the expansion of God's kingdom.",
  "prayer_en": "Lord, Nero's persecution could not burn up Your gospel. Strengthen all believers under pressure and persecution, and make me firmly trust Your kingdom surpasses all the world's powers. Amen.",
