  "prayer": "主啊，以拜尼土是亚西亚初结的果子。求祢使我有勇气作群体中第一个归向祢的人，以我的信带动后来者。阿们。",
  "lesson_en": "The firstfruits, the beloved",
  "summary_en": "The first in Asia to come to Christ, Paul's beloved.",
  "witness_en": "Epaenetus was Paul's 'beloved,' called the 'firstfruits of Asia to Christ.' He was the first person in that area to believe—the firstfruits often takes more courage, and is especially cherished by God and people.",
