  "summary_en": "A kinsman of Paul.",
  "witness_en": "Herodion was one of the 'kin' Paul greeted in Romans. A blood kinsman who also became a member in the Lord, this double bond was specially recorded by the apostle. When family can be together in the Lord, that family affection is lifted to an eternal brotherly love.",
